import React, { Fragment } from "react"; import Header from "../../shared/header/Header"; import Submenu from "../../layouts/submenu-layout/SubmenuLayout"; import "./SandW.scss"; const SandW = (props) => { return (

{props.name}

{props.days}

{props.lesson}

{props.module}

Speaking&Writing Modul # Lesson #

Recommendations

Student should send a recording after completing at least ten lessons.{" "}

Remember that you have to record all 3 parts of Speaking and:

- use paragraphing

- speak at least 2 min, but do not exceed 3 min in Speaking Part 2

- use synonyms (try to not repeat the same words)

- use different grammatical structures

1) file *.doc selected
2) file *.doc selected
3) file *.doc selected
4) file *.doc selected
5) file *.doc selected
6) file *.doc selected
7) file *.doc selected
8) file *.doc selected
9) file *.doc selected
10) file *.doc selected

Your approximate results

F/C Gr/A L/R Pr
0.0 0.0 0.0 0.0
); }; export default SandW;
